text: Hey, does anyone know if it's possible to get a Developer Account with Operations Hub? I want to have a separate development environment from the customers portal, so I don't collide with ongoing previews in the staging environment (customers sandbox).

Does anyone have a workaround to fill the field companyname in the contact section with existing data from the company section without having to register for a pro account?
